</a>
<a href="#video-link" data-video-id="dhjj4n" data-video-descrip="Normally, boss subtitles are presented *before* a boss battle and it's no different in the &amp;quot;The Legend of Heroes: Trails of Cold Steel&amp;quot; games. So when the subtitle &amp;quot;Enforcer No. 1: McBurn, the Blazing Demon&amp;quot; appears after your party has just *completed* a knock-down, drag out fight with him, you know they're in serious doo-doo..." data-video-title="McBurn, the Blazing Demon" data-video-url="https://d1w6li7s85ibls.cloudfront.net/qvbr/dhjj4n_640x360p_qvbr.mp4" data-video-thumbnail="https://static.tvtropes.org/trope_videos_transcoded/images/sd/dhjj4n.jpg" data-video-trope="Main/BossSubtitles" data-video-tropename="Boss Subtitles" data-video-approval="APPROVED" data-video-troper-rating="" data-video-average-rating="" data-video-rating-count="" data-video-media-sources="VideoGame/TheLegendOfHeroesTrailsOfColdSteel" class="video-launch-link video-overlay-link video-background-image lazy-image" data-src="https://static.tvtropes.org/trope_videos_transcoded/images/sd/dhjj4n.jpg">
